      "parameters": [
        {
          "name": "inPlugin",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "The authorization plug-in reference you assigned to the plug-in in the "
                },
                {
                  "type": "reference",
                  "isActive": true,
                  "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/security/1543160-authorizationplugincreate"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " function."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "inEngine",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "An opaque handle that you must pass back to the authorization engine when you call one of the engineâ€™s callback functions."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "mechanismId",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "The mechanism ID specified in the authorization policy database is passed to the plug-in so that the plug-in can create the appropriate mechanism. "
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "outMechanism",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "On output, points to an authorization mechanism reference that you define. The authorization engine includes this reference when it calls your plug-in so that you can identify which instance of a mechanism to invoke, deactivate, or destroy."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "content",
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "return_value",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Return Value",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "A result code. Return "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/security/1540004-authorization_services_result_co/errauthorizationsuccess"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " (no error) if the function completes successfully and "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/security/1540004-authorization_services_result_co/errauthorizationinternal"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " (Security Server internal error) if any error occurs."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "content",
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "discussion",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "A given authorization plug-in can implement any number of authorization mechanisms, distinguished by their mechanism names in the authorization policy database."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "When the authorization engine calls your "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/security/authorizationplugininterface/1543181-mechanismcreate"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " function, you should create a mechanism of the type specified by the mechanismID parameter and return an authorization mechanism reference. Subsequently, the authorization engine can call your "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/security/authorizationplugininterface/1543158-mechanisminvoke"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " function to perform an authorization, or can direct you to deactivate or destroy the mechanism instance by calling your "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/security/authorizationplugininterface/1543166-mechanismdeactivate"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " or "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/security/authorizationplugininterface/1543156-mechanismdestroy"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " functions. "
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
